<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>Vos informations de connexion</title>
    </head>
    <body style="margin:0;background:#f6f7fb;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#1f2937;">
        <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 16px;">
            <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:12px;padding:24px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;">Afriocean fish Gestion</p>
                <h1 style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:22px;line-height:1.25;color:#111827;">Vos informations de connexion</h1>

                <p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">Bonjour {{ recipient.displayName }},</p>
                <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
                    {{ actor.displayName }} vous a transmis vos accès à l’application Afriocean fish Gestion.
                </p>

                <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:14px;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#64748b;width:170px;">Prénom</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#111827;">{{ recipient.firstName ?: '-' }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#64748b;">Nom</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#111827;">{{ recipient.lastName ?: '-' }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#64748b;">Email de connexion</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#111827;">{{ recipient.email }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#64748b;">Mot de passe</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#111827;font-family:Consolas,Monaco,monospace;">{{ plain_password }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#64748b;">Lien de connexion</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#111827;">{{ application_url }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#64748b;">Rôle</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#111827;">{{ role_label }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#64748b;">Modules</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;color:#111827;">{{ module_names is empty ? 'Aucun module attribué' : module_names|join(', ') }}</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <p style="margin:20px 0 0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:#64748b;">
                    Ce mot de passe vient d’être généré pour votre compte. Nous vous recommandons de le conserver dans un endroit sécurisé.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
